<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>We are writing to let you know that your insurance will be automatically renewed on DD/MM/YEAR.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Your renewal will be </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">based on the information you provided last year</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> and your official renewal </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">quotation will follow within the next 14 days</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If any of your circumstances or requirements have changed since you last purchased your insurance, or you have made a claim or are aware of any circumstances that might lead to a claim, please call one of our Client Services Team on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> so they can make any necessary amendments and reissue a renewal quotation.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><br><b>Your Renewal Payment<br></b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b>Payment will be taken using the same method and details you provided last year. If you would like to change these please contact us on the number above.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>If you pay by direct debit </b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">- Your first direct debit for your renewal will be requested up to 10 days prior to your renewal, but will not be taken until your renewal date.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>If you pay by debit/credit card </b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">- Payment will be collected on or around 5 days before your renewal date and can take a few days to clear.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><br><b>Why renew with Kingsbridge?</b></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""></p><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Retroactive cover for previous work</b> you completed before you were insured with Kingsbridge.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b><a href="https://www.feefo.com/en-GB/reviews/kingsbridge-contractor-insurance?displayFeedbackType=SERVICE&amp;timeFrame=YEAR">Outstanding customer service</a></b> with a 4.8/5 average Feefo rating from over 10,000 customers.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">A <b>complete package of cover </b>for your business, including Professional Indemnity, Public Liability and Employers' Liability cover.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">We're not on comparison sites and our <b>prices are the same for all customers</b>, whether you're new to us or not. If you do find comparable cover for cheaper elsewhere, we'll price match it.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Additional <b>products designed for contractors</b> such as our award winning <b><a href="https://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/products/legal-ir35-protect-cover/">IR35 Protect cover</a></b>.</font></li></ul><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">If you have any questions regarding your renewal or the information above, please don't hesitate to get in touch on <b>01242 808740</b>. We look forward to another year together.<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>